 (2,'Eggs With Crab Dip','This classic New Orleans dish is perfect for a Mardi Gras party appetizer!','1. In a large mixing bowl, add the mayonnaise, mustard, lemon juice and zest, hot sauce and salt and pepper to taste. Whisk until smooth. Add the shallots, chives, capers, tarragon, and egg. Mix to combine. Add the crab and gently fold to combine.
